# Passenger <%= integration_mode_name_as_passenger_suffix %> YUM repository (.rpm packages)

We provide YUM/RPM repositories for installing Passenger on Red Hat Enterprise Linux and CentOS systems. There are separate repositories for the open source and Enterprise versions.

<% if integration_mode_type == :nginx %>
  If you use these packages to install Passenger then you do not need to run `passenger-install-nginx-module`. These packages contain all the binaries that you need, including a Passenger-enabled Nginx binary. These packages also come with SELinux policy modules so that Passenger works nicely with SELinux.
<% elsif integration_mode_type == :apache %>
  If you use these packages to install Passenger then you do not need to run `passenger-install-apache2-module`. These packages contain all the binaries that you need. These packages also come with SELinux policy modules so that Passenger works nicely with SELinux.
<% end %>

