## Background information and release policy

### Always up-to-date

Our packages are automatically built by our build server after we push out a source release, and thus are always up to date with the official source releases.

### Limited architectures

Packages are available for the x86 and x86_64 architectures only.

### Supported distribution versions

Our policy is to support all Red Hat and CentOS releases that still receive full updates by their vendors. The earliest Red Hat and CentOS version we support is version 6.
